title: One Man Who Can Save New York with Nigel Farage
itunes:title: One Man Who Can Save New York with Nigel Farage
description:
With only two weeks until one of the most important midterm elections in American history, Charlie breaks down the most important races heating up across the country, starting with New York. Could the deep blue Empire State become a Republican pick up as the state and all-important NYC suffer through a crime wave and tyrannical Albany edicts forcing thousands of New Yorkers to pack their bags and leave for other states? He’s also joined by longtime friend of show and the leader of BREXIT, Nigel Farage, to warn listeners about the cautionary tale of how to squander a conservative populist movement. Find out why Liz Truss was the victim of what Nigel calls a "globalist coup."

Support the show: http://www.charliekirk.com/support
